Class ForwardToView

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • java.lang.RuntimeException
          • org.kohsuke.stapler.ForwardToView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, HttpResponse

    public class ForwardToView
extends RuntimeException
implements HttpResponse
    HttpResponse that forwards to a RequestDispatcher, such as a view. Extends from RuntimeException so that you can throw it.
    Author:
    Kohsuke Kawaguchi
